summary.title: Class Activity 2 - Threat Modeling: Data Flow Diagram
summary.description:
Activity Objectives
Identify DFD syntax and logic errors
Apply correct modeling standards

Instruction
Use OWASP Threat Dragon to recreate the reference data flow diagram.

Tasks:
Use the appropriate symbols for each element.
Correct any errors present in the reference diagram.
Note: Threats and Scores/Priority Levels are not included in this activity.
